🌿 Vital Élan 🌿
A Serene Soundscape and Scripture Experience
Vital Élan is an elegant, spiritually inspired web application that combines soothing soundscapes with sacred scripture, creating a tranquil environment for reflection, meditation, and peace.

🌟 Features
🎶 Immersive Soundscapes: A collection of calming audio landscapes designed to promote peace and mindfulness.

📖 Sacred Scriptures: Each soundscape is paired with carefully selected scripture, offering spiritual guidance and reflection.

✨ Elegant Design: A minimalist, visually pleasing interface that enhances your spiritual journey.

🌌 Close Ritual: A “Close Ritual” button to reset the experience and end sound playback, bringing a peaceful closure to each session.
